<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Contempt" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Contempt,</orth> 1) the act of despising, disdain: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.258" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 258</bibl> (O. Edd. <emph>content</emph>). <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 174</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.109" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 109</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.149" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 149</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.164" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 164</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.2.34" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 5.3.48" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.158" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 158</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 189</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 189</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.183" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.4.117" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 4, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.209" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 209</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.173" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 173</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.124" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 210</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 210</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.309" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 309</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 42</bibl> Plural <cit><quote>--s:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 34</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.2.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 2, 127</bibl>. Followed by <emph>of,</emph> to express the thing despised: <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 4, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 8</bibl>. <cit><quote>hold in c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.80" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 80</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>placed in c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.307" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 307</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>put into c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.4.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 4, 92</bibl></cit>. <emph>in c.</emph> == contemptuously: <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.2.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 2, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 4, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.208" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 208</bibl>. <emph>in c. of question</emph> == without doubt, <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 97</bibl>. <emph>in c. of man</emph> == in spite of humanity, <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 8</bibl>.<lb />2) the state of being despised: <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.223" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 223</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.172" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 1, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 2, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 2, 15</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 27</bibl>.
<lb />Misapplied: <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.191" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 191</bibl>.
